name: SiD
wikiSummary: There are at least seven artists named SID: 1) SID (シド) is a visual-kei indies band, consisting of Mao (vocals), Shinji (guitar), Aki (bass), and Yuuya (drums). SID has currently sold out every single and album released so far, and their last two singles have placed in the Oricon Top 30 music charts. 2) Sid Hille, called Sid, is a german pianist who lives in Finland. Sid plays piano songs and has published four CDs: Dunjin's Dance (1993), To be Frank (1997), Deep North - the quiet Place (1997) and Reflections (1998). In November 1997 Sid formed the Platypus Ensemble, a Finnish jazz band. Read more about SiD on Last.fm.
